{"tid":1988238,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁凱晴：刑毀藍絲與警揮手","createTime":"2020-04-25T05:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5729c6441aae88b0ce7087f21e4fe87f8d1d5c7d","tid":1988238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/SLVBBGR3F2EADTX5G4HQOUXE2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FSLVBBGR3F2EADTX5G4HQOUXE2M%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKr0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=32ae501f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FSLVBBGR3F2EADTX5G4HQOUXE2M%2F&h=647ad1bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/SLVBBGR3F2EADTX5G4HQOUXE2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n梁凱晴：刑毀藍絲與警揮手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200425/large/1587749719_5c81.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200425%2Flarge%2F1587749719_5c81.gif&h=b0ffa8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一疑犯（箭嘴示）被指向警員揮手。梁凱晴facebook專頁<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼7.21元朗警員與白衣人拍膊示好，近日再有警員與不法分子揮手打招呼。民主派觀塘區議員梁凱晴昨於facebook專頁上載片段，指4月10日凌晨1時半至2時，有六人蓄意破壞她貼在月華街三處共八塊的宣傳橫幅，甚至自高空丟棄。當晚因木板被毀發出巨響，驚動街坊並拍下片段，顯示有疑犯曾行經警車，其中一人更向距約50米的軍裝警互相揮手打招呼。梁指疑犯動作聲響甚大，警察沒可能聽不到，質疑警方因政見而包庇罪案，甚至有勾結罪犯之嫌。警方昨未回覆查詢。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：出獄半年 邵家臻組「石牆花」護囚權<br />\n<br />\n梁凱晴在片段拍攝時間約40分鐘後報警，案件由片段中同一班軍裝警員處理，但警員對有疑犯走過隻字不提。當梁提出升降機有閉路電視或拍攝到疑犯樣貌時，警員卻扮懵反指有閉路電視「代表啲咩呢？」案發至今兩星期，未見警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200425/large/1587749718_738c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200425%2Flarge%2F1587749718_738c.gif&h=9b12ba4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁凱晴昨於facebook提出質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n質疑包庇未跟進<br />\n<br />\n梁質疑犯案過程有組織有預謀，她認為有三個可能性，若警員不認識兇徒又不知道50米外有罪案發生，便應安排警方例行驗耳驗記憶力。若警認識兇徒，料因政見相同而默許罪案，亦有可能根本是同黨。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳詠恩"},{"pid":"1f0a18ae74a15aa382e5fbf06c213b39cc484ff6","tid":1988238,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"勾結"},{"pid":"e08d2cec8aca9b1614b382c87e9a8041a734c5db","tid":1988238,"uid":29802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ddebd2fb404ea39258a206ee302b7ff0148e63","tid":1988238,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"公職人員行為失當？"},{"pid":"9c2574f2814e4b52ee496f3d813f1ea441bfdce1","tid":1988238,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff625caf4d498f7daef2ef6b401bd3e1defb4259","tid":1988238,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b6cbfb57eaed9751e4514577007272f4401d98","tid":1988238,"uid":286038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"刑毀藍絲都係警曱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7c0be301a5a20539556546d639323b3f2f04cd","tid":1988238,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgm